race.description: Bet With Betdeluxe App 5Th Grade H
race.comment: ART OF DECEPTION (2) had been in super honest form hitting the frame two times on end before finishing seventh (31.16) at Q Parklands last time. Solid record here including five wins. Form from her last run is proving to be solid. Has winning claims on her best figures. MOET MAGIC (1) was popular in betting last start but disappointed when 13 lengths away in fifth (31.22). Finished second the start before. Has a strong record from this draw, notching two wins and five minor placings from seven starts. Should be thereabouts. ZABDON IS BACK (7) showed strong early pace and stuck on well despite finishing out of the placings when fifth over 352m Q Lakeside in 20.03. Must be included in calculations. BUG ME NOT (5) has been freshened and can sneak into the frame on her best form.
